    "We measure the performance of FlowGAT in terms of three metrics of Precision, Recall, and F1 for the binary predictions (Fig. 2D).",
    "The predictions of the FlowGAT regressor manage to keep both precision and recall above 75% and 90%, respectively.",
    "To better understand the performance of our model, we compared the output of FlowGAT trained as a regressor (Fig. 2C) with those from FBA applied to the genes that appear in the MFG.",
